1
00:00:03,867 --> 00:00:06,300
Mr. Torrecampo,
your housekeeper has escaped.

2
00:00:06,433 --> 00:00:07,167
What?

3
00:00:07,300 --> 00:00:09,633
Miss? What are you doing here?

4
00:00:09,767 --> 00:00:14,100
I deeply regret
the wrong I did to Marj.

5
00:00:14,233 --> 00:00:19,000
Ma'am Marj. I want to help you
find a donor for Jasmine.

6
00:00:19,133 --> 00:00:20,333
Look!

7
00:00:20,467 --> 00:00:21,867
A paternity test?

8
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,933
Look at who is listed
as the mother and father there.

9
00:00:25,067 --> 00:00:26,433
[CLAMORING]

10
00:00:26,567 --> 00:00:28,800
That suits you! You demon!

11
00:00:28,933 --> 00:00:31,100
You have been deceiving me
for sixteen years!

12
00:00:31,233 --> 00:00:32,900
Marj,
what are you talking about?

13
00:00:33,033 --> 00:00:36,067
Ashley is the child
of Thea and Paolo!

14
00:01:25,867 --> 00:01:28,067
- Careful on the last step.
- Yes, yes. I will be.

15
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:31,200
Congratulations to you!
You solved your problem!

16
00:01:31,333 --> 00:01:32,833
[WHOOPS]
[CHUCKLES]

17
00:01:32,967 --> 00:01:35,033
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

18
00:01:35,167 --> 00:01:37,467
I do not know why
I did not think of it before.

19
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,867
What I needed to do
was actually very simple.

20
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:45,300
[INTENSE MUSIC]

21
00:01:45,467 --> 00:01:48,400
And I should say,
that was very clever of you.

22
00:01:48,533 --> 00:01:51,000
Like a dark enchantress
sneaking in the dead of night.

23
00:01:51,133 --> 00:01:52,400
Impressive!

24
00:01:52,533 --> 00:02:02,500
[INTENSE MUSIC]

25
00:02:04,167 --> 00:02:05,767
You're impressive.

26
00:02:07,267 --> 00:02:08,933
You know, one of these days,

27
00:02:09,067 --> 00:02:11,500
I will introduce you
to my father.

28
00:02:11,633 --> 00:02:13,167
I am sure you will get along.

29
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:15,767
Oh, the senior Mr. Castelo?

30
00:02:15,933 --> 00:02:18,600
Well, Castelo
is my mother's maiden name.

31
00:02:18,733 --> 00:02:21,900
My dad is more
on the low-key side.

32
00:02:22,033 --> 00:02:23,067
Very refreshing.

33
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:26,267
Someone who doesn't need
to show off.

34
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:29,333
Anyway, I am sorry
to keep this exchange short.

35
00:02:29,467 --> 00:02:31,000
But I really need
my beauty rest.

36
00:02:31,133 --> 00:02:33,533
But I will finish this first,
okay?

37
00:02:33,667 --> 00:02:36,067
I am really looking forward
to meeting your father.

38
00:02:37,167 --> 00:02:40,600
I want to finally meet
the person who inspires you.

39
00:02:40,733 --> 00:02:42,800
Yes, and I am very excited
for you to meet him.

40
00:02:42,933 --> 00:02:45,167
Because you know him very well,
Regina.

41
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:46,800
Very well.

42
00:02:46,933 --> 00:02:56,900
[INTENSE MUSIC]

43
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,900
Sir. Sir, wait!

44
00:03:03,033 --> 00:03:04,633
Where are you taking me?

45
00:03:04,767 --> 00:03:06,000
You're so stubborn!

46
00:03:06,133 --> 00:03:07,967
To the prosecutor,
for an inquest proceeding.

47
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:09,767
I need to call
my employer first.

48
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:12,200
Ma'am Marj! She needs to know
the truth, Sir!

49
00:03:12,333 --> 00:03:14,467
Did you not already use
your call to your niece earlier?

50
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:16,400
Why did you not
call Marj instead?

51
00:03:16,533 --> 00:03:18,567
- Get in! Get in!
- Please.

52
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:28,667
[INTENSE MUSIC]

53
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:36,733
Do we really all need
to be here?

54
00:03:38,267 --> 00:03:39,600
Of course, Mom.

55
00:03:39,733 --> 00:03:42,567
Jasmine needs all the prayers.

56
00:03:42,700 --> 00:03:47,000
[PENSIVE MUSIC]

57
00:03:47,133 --> 00:03:48,267
Jas?

58
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:57,700
[PENSIVE MUSIC]

59
00:03:57,867 --> 00:04:00,333
Are we ready to start?
Can we begin?

60
00:04:00,467 --> 00:04:03,467
[PENSIVE MUSIC]

61
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:07,600
Pascual, take my place for now.
I'll do a round at the back.

62
00:04:07,733 --> 00:04:08,933
Roger, Sir. Copy, Sir.

63
00:04:12,333 --> 00:04:22,300
[INTENSE MUSIC]

64
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:25,333
Everyone,
please gather around Jasmine.

65
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:28,867
Father, please. Can you start?

66
00:04:29,033 --> 00:04:30,633
Okay, is everyone ready?

67
00:04:32,867 --> 00:04:36,200
In the name of the Father,
the Son, and the Holy Spirit.

68
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:42,900
Lord, we lift Jasmine to You.

69
00:04:43,033 --> 00:04:45,833
Heal her body.

70
00:04:45,967 --> 00:04:46,967
Hello, Mom.

71
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:49,600
Did I not tell you I had
straight duty last night?

72
00:04:49,733 --> 00:04:52,867
And now you are imagining
things again.

73
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,967
Here, I am heading home now.

74
00:04:55,100 --> 00:04:59,933
Calm her fears and let her feel
Your presence right now.

75
00:05:00,067 --> 00:05:06,467
As a family, we may offer our
personal prayers for Jasmine.

76
00:05:06,633 --> 00:05:08,267
Please begin, Ma'am.

77
00:05:09,867 --> 00:05:11,300
Lord,

78
00:05:11,433 --> 00:05:13,433
we lift up Jasmine to You.

79
00:05:13,567 --> 00:05:18,800
Please let her feel Your
presence so she may grow strong.

80
00:05:18,933 --> 00:05:21,033
Mend the cracks around her

81
00:05:21,167 --> 00:05:23,767
because it will be hard
for her to recover

82
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:27,433
if the people she depends on

83
00:05:27,567 --> 00:05:30,533
are not in good terms
with each other

84
00:05:30,667 --> 00:05:33,433
and are filled with bitterness
toward one another.

85
00:05:35,233 --> 00:05:40,667
Lord, please cleanse
the air in our home

86
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:44,000
and shake off
any negative energy

87
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:52,500
that keeps disturbing
and dividing our family.

88
00:05:55,100 --> 00:06:02,533
Please also teach us
to have respect for one another

89
00:06:02,667 --> 00:06:06,733
because how can we ask
for a miracle for Jasmine

90
00:06:06,867 --> 00:06:08,600
if the foundation of our home

91
00:06:08,767 --> 00:06:12,500
is built on pride
and lack of respect?

92
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,800
And lastly, Lord,

93
00:06:18,933 --> 00:06:21,633
please restore the bonds
that have been broken

94
00:06:21,767 --> 00:06:24,267
by shallow things.

95
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:27,033
How can we ask
for Jasmine's recovery

96
00:06:27,167 --> 00:06:30,733
if there are walls
standing between us?

97
00:06:30,867 --> 00:06:40,833
[INTENSE MUSIC]

98
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:43,867
Let her courage shine.

99
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,633
Let Your light break through

100
00:06:45,767 --> 00:06:50,133
every shadow of hatred and
doubt.

101
00:06:50,267 --> 00:06:51,433
Miss?

102
00:06:51,567 --> 00:06:54,467
We ask this through Your Son,
Jesus Christ.

103
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:56,100
Amen.

104
00:06:56,233 --> 00:07:06,200
[INTENSE MUSIC]

105
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,267
Cheche!

106
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,233
Wait a moment!

107
00:07:11,367 --> 00:07:13,633
Cheche!

108
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:16,433
Oh, your grilled food.
Go to it later.

109
00:07:16,567 --> 00:07:18,767
No, because Ma'am Regina
is calling for you.

110
00:07:18,900 --> 00:07:20,833
You need to go to her now.
Hurry!

111
00:07:21,900 --> 00:07:23,533
No, you are being rushed
already. Go now!

112
00:07:23,667 --> 00:07:25,500
You might get scolded. Go on!

113
00:07:25,633 --> 00:07:33,300
[INTENSE MUSIC]

114
00:07:33,433 --> 00:07:34,500
Miss?

115
00:07:34,633 --> 00:07:44,400
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

116
00:07:44,533 --> 00:07:45,933
Ms. Yolly.

117
00:07:46,067 --> 00:07:48,967
Miss, what are you doing here?

118
00:07:49,133 --> 00:07:50,967
Do you want Ma'am Regina
to catch you?

119
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,567
Weng, I need to talk
to Ma'am Marj.

120
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:55,300
Can you help me?

121
00:07:55,433 --> 00:07:57,300
I need to get
close to her.

122
00:07:57,433 --> 00:07:58,967
Please, Weng.

123
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:00,033
What?

124
00:08:00,167 --> 00:08:06,267
[INTENSE MUSIC]

125
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:07,367
Evelyn told me about

126
00:08:07,500 --> 00:08:10,333
what you and your spouse
are going through.

127
00:08:10,467 --> 00:08:12,567
As your relative, Marj,

128
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:15,267
I am also praying
that you overcome

129
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,700
the problems you are facing.

130
00:08:17,833 --> 00:08:24,333
Father, I deeply regret
the wrong I did to Marj.

131
00:08:26,033 --> 00:08:32,000
But it feels like I do not know
if Marj can still forgive me.

132
00:08:33,467 --> 00:08:35,467
Forgiveness is easy to speak of.

133
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:38,967
But you cannot force me to do it
right away.

134
00:08:39,100 --> 00:08:42,367
What I do not know is whether I
can still trust my spouse again.

135
00:08:42,500 --> 00:08:43,767
You are right, Marj.

136
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:46,067
Forgiveness is godly.

137
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,667
But it takes time

138
00:08:47,800 --> 00:08:50,700
to free yourself
from the prison of anger.

139
00:08:50,833 --> 00:08:55,433
And forgiving does not mean
you will forget the pain

140
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,567
caused by betrayal.

141
00:08:58,900 --> 00:09:03,533
That is where Marj's struggle
to trust again comes in.

142
00:09:04,667 --> 00:09:07,933
You need to earn
your spouse's trust again.

143
00:09:08,067 --> 00:09:11,633
And I am warning you,
this will not be easy.

144
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,067
And Marj,

145
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,500
for the peace of your heart,

146
00:09:18,633 --> 00:09:27,033
give Paolo the chance to prove
remorse and to correct mistakes.

147
00:09:37,733 --> 00:09:38,833
Hey.

148
00:09:38,967 --> 00:09:40,033
I am sorry I am late.

149
00:09:42,033 --> 00:09:44,033
Why did Ashley not text you?

150
00:09:45,267 --> 00:09:47,500
You are close, right?

151
00:09:47,633 --> 00:09:49,600
Like super close.

152
00:09:51,233 --> 00:09:53,133
Not as close as you think.

153
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,933
Yes, I do like her.

154
00:09:58,733 --> 00:10:00,000
But only up to that point.

155
00:10:01,467 --> 00:10:04,200
There is nothing
between Ash and me.

156
00:10:06,100 --> 00:10:08,333
Actually...

157
00:10:08,467 --> 00:10:09,967
she rejected me.

158
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,600
What?

159
00:10:12,733 --> 00:10:14,733
She cares about you so much

160
00:10:14,867 --> 00:10:16,300
that she does not want
you to get hurt.

161
00:10:16,433 --> 00:10:18,533
So, should I thank her?

162
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:22,367
Because she gave you up
even though she likes you too?

163
00:10:23,633 --> 00:10:26,033
Do you know how insulting
that is for me?

164
00:10:27,067 --> 00:10:28,367
You know what?

165
00:10:28,500 --> 00:10:30,233
I get it.

166
00:10:30,367 --> 00:10:33,067
Even I would not like myself.

167
00:10:34,500 --> 00:10:36,033
Because I am sick.

168
00:10:37,233 --> 00:10:40,867
Ugly, weak,
not fun to be with.

169
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,400
That is not true, Jas.

170
00:10:42,533 --> 00:10:43,733
But it is.

171
00:10:43,867 --> 00:10:46,600
I am just a burdento everyone.

172
00:10:46,733 --> 00:10:48,233
I am dying.

173
00:10:48,367 --> 00:10:50,767
So why would
you choose me?

174
00:10:52,633 --> 00:10:53,833
Jas,

175
00:10:55,133 --> 00:10:57,400
I care about you.

176
00:10:57,533 --> 00:10:59,867
I am not lying.
It is just that...

177
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:04,400
I really only see you
as a friend.

178
00:11:11,133 --> 00:11:12,133
You know what?

179
00:11:12,267 --> 00:11:14,600
I do not need your stupid pity.

180
00:11:14,733 --> 00:11:16,800
So can you just leave?

181
00:11:16,933 --> 00:11:18,800
Leave.

182
00:11:18,933 --> 00:11:20,433
- Jas.
- Just leave.

183
00:11:38,900 --> 00:11:40,100
Marj.

184
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:45,000
Father told me
to give you a chance.

185
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:50,867
We have vows as spouses that we
should overcome this problem.

186
00:11:52,233 --> 00:11:54,333
How can I give you
a second chance...

187
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:58,933
when all I feel toward you
is anger and resentment?

188
00:11:59,967 --> 00:12:02,167
Let out your anger.

189
00:12:02,300 --> 00:12:03,833
Hurt me.

190
00:12:03,967 --> 00:12:05,767
Shout at me.

191
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:08,767
- Slap me.
- Paolo.

192
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:11,467
I will accept anything.

193
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:14,300
Even if I hurt you,
what would it be for?

194
00:12:14,467 --> 00:12:16,567
What if you do it again?

195
00:12:16,700 --> 00:12:18,767
What if you hurt me again?

196
00:12:18,900 --> 00:12:22,200
What if you break
my trust again?

197
00:12:22,333 --> 00:12:24,500
Paolo, I am tired of being hurt.

198
00:12:25,567 --> 00:12:29,000
I am tired of you making me hope
you will change.

199
00:12:29,133 --> 00:12:30,567
Marj, please.

200
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,200
Please.

201
00:12:32,333 --> 00:12:34,700
I will do everything.
Just trust me.

202
00:12:34,833 --> 00:12:37,067
Let me go.

203
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:41,167
- Paolo, please, let me go.
- No.

204
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:44,400
No. I will do everything.

205
00:12:44,533 --> 00:12:46,800
I will do absolutely everything
so you can forgive me,

206
00:12:46,933 --> 00:12:48,400
so we can be okay again.

207
00:12:48,567 --> 00:12:54,867
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

208
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:57,300
I love you so much.
Why did you hurt me like this?

209
00:12:57,433 --> 00:12:59,633
Why did you deceive me?

210
00:12:59,767 --> 00:13:01,200
Why did you do this to me?

211
00:13:01,333 --> 00:13:03,967
You know I love you so much.

212
00:13:04,100 --> 00:13:08,733
- Why did you do this?
- I am really sorry.

213
00:13:08,867 --> 00:13:10,233
I am so sorry.

214
00:13:10,367 --> 00:13:11,467
I really mean it.

215
00:13:11,600 --> 00:13:14,067
I am so sorry.
I truly regret it.

216
00:13:20,533 --> 00:13:22,533
Just promise me again.

217
00:13:24,333 --> 00:13:27,767
Promise me again that you
will not hurt me again, okay?

218
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:30,300
Do not lie to me again.

219
00:13:32,833 --> 00:13:34,433
I promise.

220
00:13:34,567 --> 00:13:36,267
I promise, Marj.

221
00:13:37,267 --> 00:13:47,233
[OST PLAYING]

222
00:13:55,933 --> 00:13:57,033
Hello.

223
00:13:57,167 --> 00:13:59,100
Ah, hello, Mr. Torrecampo.

224
00:13:59,233 --> 00:14:01,867
This is Police Major Santos.

225
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:05,433
Major, is there an update
on the case against Yolly?

226
00:14:05,567 --> 00:14:10,400
I am calling to inform you that
your housekeeper has escaped.

227
00:14:10,533 --> 00:14:12,633
What?

228
00:14:12,767 --> 00:14:14,433
Oscar!

229
00:14:14,567 --> 00:14:15,767
Oscar!

230
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:18,633
Oscar!

231
00:14:18,767 --> 00:14:20,367
You are completely useless!

232
00:14:21,533 --> 00:14:22,867
Sir! Sir Greg!

233
00:14:24,667 --> 00:14:29,300
Order our guards to secure
the perimeter of the house!

234
00:14:29,467 --> 00:14:31,800
Yolly has escaped!

235
00:14:31,933 --> 00:14:34,733
Make sure she cannot
enter this house.

236
00:14:34,867 --> 00:14:36,433
She will surely retaliate.

237
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,800
Yes, Sir Greg!

238
00:14:38,933 --> 00:14:48,900
[INTENSE MUSIC]

239
00:14:55,033 --> 00:14:56,067
Ma'am Marj.

240
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,667
Ma'am Marj.

241
00:15:01,300 --> 00:15:03,367
- Ms. Yolly?
- Come here.

242
00:15:03,533 --> 00:15:12,333
[INTENSE MUSIC]

243
00:15:12,467 --> 00:15:15,500
- What are you doing here?
- Do not be loud. Just trust me.

244
00:15:15,633 --> 00:15:17,633
- Come on.
- What? But, Ms. Yolly.

245
00:15:19,367 --> 00:15:21,567
Father,
since you are already here,

246
00:15:21,700 --> 00:15:23,267
maybe you can bless the house.

247
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,300
You know, it was from a fire.

248
00:15:25,433 --> 00:15:28,633
I heard it from my cousin,
Marj's mother.

249
00:15:30,800 --> 00:15:36,200
You know, not everything
dies in a fire.

250
00:15:36,367 --> 00:15:39,467
Like bad spirits and old sins,

251
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:43,633
and the monsters
living under the same roof.

252
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:52,900
This is not necessary,
Mrs. Torrecampo.

253
00:15:53,033 --> 00:15:55,000
That is my donation
to the parish.

254
00:15:56,033 --> 00:15:57,733
Thank you.

255
00:15:57,867 --> 00:16:01,600
Paolo, come here.
Father will bless the house now.

256
00:16:01,733 --> 00:16:03,400
- Come along.
- All right.

257
00:16:03,533 --> 00:16:05,733
Ashley, come here.

258
00:16:05,867 --> 00:16:08,367
Che, where is your Ma'am Marj?

259
00:16:08,533 --> 00:16:10,967
Sir, I did not see her either.
I do not know.

260
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:12,333
Where is she?

261
00:16:12,467 --> 00:16:15,500
Sir, maybe she just went
to the bathroom.

262
00:16:16,733 --> 00:16:19,100
All right, come on.
Come on, Father.

263
00:16:19,233 --> 00:16:21,200
Let's go. Come on, Ashley.

264
00:16:24,667 --> 00:16:26,867
Ms. Yolly,
what are you doing?

265
00:16:27,000 --> 00:16:29,567
- I escaped from the police.
- What?

266
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:31,467
Wait, I did not hurt you.

267
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:34,367
I have only wanted to help you
since the other day.

268
00:16:36,067 --> 00:16:37,600
This is what we need
to talk about.

269
00:16:37,733 --> 00:16:41,600
I want to help you
find a donor for Jasmine.

270
00:16:41,767 --> 00:16:42,933
And aside from that,

271
00:16:43,067 --> 00:16:46,867
I want you to know a hidden
secret of the Torrecampo family.

272
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:50,133
- What secret?
- This.

273
00:16:50,267 --> 00:16:52,000
Look at this.

274
00:16:53,267 --> 00:16:54,900
Look.

275
00:17:00,233 --> 00:17:03,133
What is this? A paternity test?

276
00:17:03,267 --> 00:17:05,433
Ninety-nine point ninety-nine
percent

277
00:17:05,567 --> 00:17:07,700
probability of paternity.

278
00:17:07,833 --> 00:17:10,167
Look. Look at who is listed
as the mother and father.

279
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,667
Thea.

280
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:16,133
Thea and Paolo.

281
00:17:16,300 --> 00:17:18,900
Ashley is their child,
Ma'am Marj.

282
00:17:19,033 --> 00:17:27,333
[INTENSE MUSIC]

283
00:17:27,467 --> 00:17:30,167
They have been deceiving you
for a long time.

284
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:33,933
They even had a child
and Sir Greg knows about it.

285
00:17:34,967 --> 00:17:35,900
What?

286
00:17:36,033 --> 00:17:39,200
They are ganging up on you,
Ma'am Marj.

287
00:17:39,333 --> 00:17:41,500
Go. Check all the rooms.

288
00:17:41,633 --> 00:17:43,300
Yolly might still be here.

289
00:17:43,433 --> 00:17:44,700
Let's go.

290
00:17:46,733 --> 00:17:49,533
Ms. Yolly, you need to leave
now. Please be careful.

291
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:51,100
You take care, okay?

292
00:17:51,233 --> 00:17:54,933
You no longer know who
you can trust in this house.

293
00:17:55,067 --> 00:17:58,200
Sir Edward was the only decent
one but he is gone too.

294
00:17:58,333 --> 00:18:00,533
So, if I were you, leave this
place with Jasmine.

295
00:18:00,667 --> 00:18:04,067
Escape from here
once she recovers.

296
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,333
Go now.

297
00:18:05,467 --> 00:18:15,433
[INTENSE MUSIC]

298
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:47,067
Let this be a place of peace,
of honesty, and protection.

299
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:51,467
Remove from this house
anything that brings harm,

300
00:18:51,600 --> 00:18:52,867
fear, and division.

301
00:18:53,000 --> 00:18:56,033
Make sure you check every
corner of the house, okay?

302
00:18:56,200 --> 00:18:57,300
Yes, Sir!

303
00:18:57,433 --> 00:18:59,033
May love be stronger than anger,

304
00:18:59,167 --> 00:19:01,433
forgiveness stronger
than resentment,

305
00:19:01,567 --> 00:19:03,500
and faith stronger than doubt.

306
00:19:03,633 --> 00:19:04,700
Marj?

307
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,467
That suits you. You demon.

308
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,833
You are a monster!

309
00:19:12,967 --> 00:19:14,267
- There!
- Stop that!

310
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,633
What is your problem
with me now?

311
00:19:15,767 --> 00:19:17,000
Marj, are you losing your mind?

312
00:19:17,133 --> 00:19:20,033
That is still not enough
for all your sins...

313
00:19:20,167 --> 00:19:21,533
Enough, stop it already!

314
00:19:21,667 --> 00:19:24,000
*

315
00:19:24,133 --> 00:19:25,433
You're an animal!

316
00:19:26,567 --> 00:19:27,700
*

317
00:19:29,167 --> 00:19:31,767
[CLAMORING]

318
00:19:31,900 --> 00:19:33,333
That suits you!

319
00:19:36,533 --> 00:19:38,067
Marj!

320
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,800
Marj, Marj!

321
00:19:39,933 --> 00:19:40,600
[CLAMORING]

322
00:19:40,733 --> 00:19:42,533
Sixteen years?

323
00:19:42,667 --> 00:19:44,867
You have been deceiving me
for sixteen years,

324
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:47,667
but I know everything now.

325
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,367
Marj, what are
you talking about?

326
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:58,033
[INTENSE MUSIC]

327
00:19:58,167 --> 00:20:00,167
[CLAMORING]

328
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,433
I did nothing to you.

329
00:20:02,600 --> 00:20:06,033
Why do you
always target me?

330
00:20:06,167 --> 00:20:09,267
[INTENSE MUSIC]

331
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:11,500
- A paternity test?
- Yes.

332
00:20:11,633 --> 00:20:13,733
Ms. Yolly gave it to me.

333
00:20:13,867 --> 00:20:16,267
These two have betrayed me
for a long time.

334
00:20:16,400 --> 00:20:19,500
[MUSIC CONTINUES]

335
00:20:19,633 --> 00:20:22,700
Ashley is the child
of Thea and Paolo.

336
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:32,800
[INTENSE MUSIC]

337
00:20:40,967 --> 00:20:43,567
Mom, is this true?

338
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:45,600
Dad, is Ash my sibling?

339
00:20:45,733 --> 00:20:53,700
[INTENSE MUSIC]

340
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:55,200
What?

341
00:20:55,333 --> 00:20:57,633
What? Answer me! Speak!

342
00:20:57,767 --> 00:21:00,367
Admit to everyone,
even to God and the priest,

343
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:04,933
how you deceived us and Edward
for so long! Speak!

344
00:21:05,067 --> 00:21:07,267
Weng, Che, please take the
children to the room for now.

345
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:10,367
No! They should all hear this!

346
00:21:10,533 --> 00:21:13,833
- Stop causing a scandal, Marj!
- You too!

347
00:21:13,967 --> 00:21:15,733
What kind of parent are you?

348
00:21:15,867 --> 00:21:17,833
Instead of teaching Paolo
to do right,

349
00:21:17,967 --> 00:21:20,200
you tolerated wrongdoing?

350
00:21:20,333 --> 00:21:21,700
To lie to me?

351
00:21:23,267 --> 00:21:24,667
You knew, Greg?

352
00:21:28,767 --> 00:21:29,733
Marj!

353
00:21:29,867 --> 00:21:32,233
What are you so furious about?

354
00:21:32,367 --> 00:21:33,433
You already caught us, right?

355
00:21:33,567 --> 00:21:35,833
Paolo and I are done.
What more do you want?

356
00:21:35,967 --> 00:21:37,433
[CLAMORING]

357
00:21:37,567 --> 00:21:38,567
- Marj, stop...
- [SLAPS]

358
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:40,033
Do not interfere here!

359
00:21:41,067 --> 00:21:43,900
No one will interfere here.

360
00:21:44,067 --> 00:21:46,700
If you do not stop,
two houses will burn.

361
00:21:46,833 --> 00:21:47,900
Marj.

362
00:21:48,033 --> 00:21:49,967
Enough! Marj, please!

363
00:21:50,100 --> 00:21:53,167
Forgive me, Father,
for what I am about to do.

364
00:21:53,300 --> 00:21:55,433
I will confess afterward.

365
00:21:55,567 --> 00:21:57,267
- Please, stop!
- Come here.

366
00:21:57,400 --> 00:21:58,800
[CLAMORING]

367
00:21:58,933 --> 00:22:00,100
Marj, wait!

368
00:22:00,233 --> 00:22:04,300
[CLAMORING]

369
00:22:13,533 --> 00:22:14,667
Marj!

370
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:15,967
Do not interfere!

371
00:22:16,133 --> 00:22:18,067
Enough, please, Marj!

372
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:19,600
Marj, stop it!

373
00:22:19,733 --> 00:22:21,300
Mercy?

374
00:22:21,433 --> 00:22:22,900
Do not interfere!

375
00:22:23,967 --> 00:22:28,867
Do you pity my child while
she is fighting her illness?

376
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:32,333
While you were enjoying
her father's body?

377
00:22:32,467 --> 00:22:34,400
Do not come near me!

378
00:22:34,533 --> 00:22:35,433
- Marj!
- Enough!

379
00:22:35,567 --> 00:22:37,933
Huh? What pity!

380
00:22:38,067 --> 00:22:39,167
Open the gate!

381
00:22:40,233 --> 00:22:43,633
Do not interfere with me!
No one will interfere!

382
00:22:43,767 --> 00:22:46,567
[CLAMORING]
I said stop it!

383
00:22:50,233 --> 00:22:51,433
Marj!

384
00:22:51,567 --> 00:22:53,933
- What is this?
- Marj, please.

385
00:22:54,067 --> 00:22:57,733
- Marj, enough! Enough!
- Do not interfere!

386
00:22:57,867 --> 00:23:00,500
Marj, stop it!
People are looking.

387
00:23:00,633 --> 00:23:03,200
Here! So, everyone can see!

388
00:23:03,333 --> 00:23:07,467
Go on, take out your phones.
I do not care!

389
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:12,667
This woman is none other
than Thea Villareal Torrecampo!

390
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:17,133
She stole my spouse
and got pregnant by him!

391
00:23:17,267 --> 00:23:19,800
Shame does not exist for her

392
00:23:19,933 --> 00:23:24,500
because she made her spouse
who is my spouse's sibling

393
00:23:24,667 --> 00:23:26,900
take responsibility
for their depravity!

394
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,500
What?

395
00:23:29,633 --> 00:23:31,600
You want me to
stop, Paolo?

396
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:35,100
There, I let go!

397
00:23:36,367 --> 00:23:39,733
Be thankful that is all you got
from me.

398
00:23:39,867 --> 00:23:41,567
I am telling you, Thea,

399
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:43,833
the moment you return
to this house,

400
00:23:43,967 --> 00:23:46,167
you will not just go viral.

401
00:23:46,300 --> 00:23:48,433
I will bury you alive.

402
00:23:48,567 --> 00:23:50,633
I will watch over your grave

403
00:23:50,767 --> 00:23:57,767
until your soul rots
which is already decaying.

404
00:23:57,933 --> 00:24:02,267
You have no right to drive
me out of that house.

405
00:24:02,400 --> 00:24:07,267
Mom, help me, please!
Please! Help me!

406
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:10,467
Mom, please,
we are on the same side, right?

407
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:13,600
I do not need another
homewrecker in my home.

408
00:24:13,733 --> 00:24:15,867
Edward should have been here.

409
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:19,900
If someone should leave
and never return, it is you.

410
00:24:20,033 --> 00:24:23,233
Mom, please,
do not do this to me...

411
00:24:23,367 --> 00:24:25,267
Dad, Dad, Dad, please!

412
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:27,000
Please! You cannot abandon me!

413
00:24:27,133 --> 00:24:30,867
I am sorry, Thea.
You did this to yourself.

414
00:24:31,033 --> 00:24:32,900
No. No. No.

415
00:24:33,033 --> 00:24:34,767
Paolo!

416
00:24:34,900 --> 00:24:37,267
Paolo, Paolo,
listen to me!

417
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,067
Paolo, help me! I need you!

418
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,067
Paolo!

419
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:42,267
Paolo, please, do not leave me.

420
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,533
Guard!

421
00:24:43,667 --> 00:24:47,267
No! No! This cannot happen!

422
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,500
Hey!

423
00:24:49,633 --> 00:24:50,733
Why?

424
00:24:50,867 --> 00:24:53,233
Paolo is also
at fault here!

425
00:24:55,567 --> 00:24:58,033
Wait, Ashley.
My child. My child.

426
00:24:58,167 --> 00:25:00,267
My child is inside.

427
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:04,700
Wait. Help me! Help me!

428
00:25:11,367 --> 00:25:12,600
What?

429
00:25:14,933 --> 00:25:17,467
Are you enjoying the show?

430
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:20,533
You losers!

431
00:25:20,667 --> 00:25:23,900
You are all useless!

432
00:25:24,033 --> 00:25:34,000
[INTENSE MUSIC]

433
00:25:40,667 --> 00:25:43,200
What did I do?

434
00:25:43,333 --> 00:25:46,667
What did I do to you for
you to treat me like this?

435
00:25:46,800 --> 00:25:51,467
You did nothing wrong. I am the
one at fault. You are right.

436
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:55,633
But Marj, I will never
stop apologizing to you.

437
00:25:55,767 --> 00:25:58,433
I will never forgive you.

438
00:25:59,733 --> 00:26:01,800
Be afraid now,
my dear husband.

439
00:26:01,933 --> 00:26:05,133
Because you are the one
with a closet full of skeletons.

440
00:26:05,267 --> 00:26:08,633
When a woman who has been silent
for a long time gets angry,

441
00:26:08,800 --> 00:26:11,400
she does not just dig up bones.

442
00:26:11,533 --> 00:26:12,867
She exhumes.

443
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:14,967
You are too complacent.

444
00:26:15,100 --> 00:26:17,767
Why?
Do you have nothing to hide?

445
00:26:18,900 --> 00:26:20,067
Wow!

446
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:22,100
If Ashley and Jasmine
are siblings,

447
00:26:22,233 --> 00:26:23,700
the chance might be high

448
00:26:23,833 --> 00:26:26,067
that they match
for a bone marrow transplant.

449
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:29,067
If you want a chance to
change my mind,

450
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,800
there is one thing
you need to do.

451
00:26:30,933 --> 00:26:33,233
Please, tell me.

452
00:26:33,367 --> 00:26:37,133
Convince Thea to allow Ashley
to get tested.

453
00:26:37,267 --> 00:26:41,300
That is all you need to do
so that is what you need to fix.
